description.narrative: In 2021, continued to focus on delivering a swift response on COVID-19 awareness raising, especially in terms of vaccine acceptance and demand generation. A total of 11 campaigns were led on COVID19, Girls empowerment/FGM, social inclusion and education, for a grand total of 257 million reach. In addition, visibility of programme was extended with more than 50 HIS story produced and more than 280 UNICEF mentions in the press. This was done in addition to strengthened efforts on raising the attention of donors and natcoms on UNICEF activities in Egypt. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:05/01/2022
